This complete MERN stack solution includes all the required features:
1. JWT authentication (login/register)
2. Product search and filtering
3. Products table with all specified columns
4. Import/export functionality
5. Inline editing
6. Inventory history tracking
7. Responsive design

The backend uses MongoDB with Mongoose for data modeling, and the frontend uses vanilla CSS for styling. The solution is ready for deployment to Render (backend) and Netlify (frontend).
